data.description: Set any request with a no "Cache-Control header" from the origin to stay on the server. Possible values are 1d, 7d, 1M, 12M

data.description: Ignore any cookies set by the origin in order to make the content consistently cacheable

data.description: Valid IP address of the Origin URL. Be sure to set dns_check to 0 to prevent this value from being overwritten.
